{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerForPushNotificationsWith:","title":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:"}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswith:"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerForPushNotificationsWith:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Registers the device for push notifications with initial tags.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"tags","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"tags","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set during registration."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Supported value types: NSString, NSNumber, NSArray (for list tags).","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Combines push notification registration with tag assignment in a single operation."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is more efficient than calling registerForPushNotifications and setTags separately,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as tags are sent to the server along with the registration request."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method when you have user attributes available at the time of registration,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as during onboarding or after user authentication."}]},{"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register with user attributes after sign-up:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class SignUpCoordinator {","","    func completeSignUp(user: User, source: SignUpSource) {","        let registrationTags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_source\": source.analyticsValue,","            \"signup_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","            \"interests\": user.selectedInterests,","            \"language\": Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\",","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(with: registrationTags)","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id)","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(user.email)","    }","}","","extension Bundle {","    var appVersion: String {","        infoDictionary?[\"CFBundleShortVersionString\"] as? String ?? \"unknown\"","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","ty